OL,6,FEarlier on Wednesday, the prime
OL,7,Fminister reacted to the criticism from
OL,8,Fa former subpostmaster, ITV News
OL,9,FReporter Chloe Keedy has the latest
OL,11,FThe government has reacted after
OL,12,Fformer subpostmaster Jo Hamilton said
OL,13,Fmany of those falsely accused during
OL,14,Fthe Horizon scandal had still not been
OL,15,Fpaid compensation.
OL,17,FMs Hamilton made the comments while
OL,18,Faddressing the audience at the
OL,19,FNational Television Awards on
OL,20,FWednesday evening.
