OL,3,CGovernment promises to deliver redress
OL,4,Cto subpostmasters amid criticism
OL,6,FShe was one of a group of real
OL,7,Fsubpostmasters who joined the cast of
OL,8,FITV drama Mr Bates vs the Post Office
OL,9,Fon stage, after they won three prizes
OL,10,Fduring the ceremony.
OL,12,FMs Hamilton, who is portrayed by
OL,13,FMonica Dolan in the series, told the
OL,14,Faudience she was disappointed by the
OL,15,Flack of movement on compensation
OL,16,Fpayments since the election.
OL,18,F"What I want you to know is that I
OL,19,Fwent to Westminster a couple of weeks
OL,20,Fback and saw the new minister," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
