OL,6,F"And trust me, nothing has changed.
OL,7,FAlmost all of these people behind me
OL,8,Fhaven't been paid yet," she added,
OL,9,Freferencing the other former
OL,10,Fsubpostmasters beside her on stage.
OL,12,FMs Hamilton said that out of a group
OL,13,Fof 555 former subpostmasters awaiting
OL,14,Fcompensation, more than 300 had not
OL,15,Fyet been paid.
OL,17,FShe added that Sir Alan Bates, the
OL,18,Fcampaign leader and focus of the
OL,19,Fdrama, was among that number.
