OL,6,F"They've offered him 30% of his
OL,7,Fclaim," she said.
OL,9,FIn response, Post Office Minister
OL,10,FGareth Thomas told ITV News that he
OL,11,Fcontinues to meet subpostmasters and
OL,12,Fpromises he is "working with them so
OL,13,Fthey get the redress they deserve".
OL,15,FHe added "almost #290 million has been
OL,16,Fpaid to over 2,800 claimants across
OL,17,Ffour compensation schemes, but we know
OL,18,Fthere is more to be done, and we are
OL,19,Fcommitted to ensuring every postmaster
OL,20,Freceives full and fair redress as
OL,21,Fquickly as possible."
