OL,3,CGovernment promises to deliver redress
OL,4,Cto subpostmasters amid criticism
OL,6,FMore than 700 subpostmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fgiven criminal convictions between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015, as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,FHorizon IT system made it appear as
OL,11,Fthough money was missing from their
OL,12,Fbranches.
OL,14,FOne former subpostmaster who is yet to
OL,15,Fbe paid, Lee Castleton, told ITV News
OL,16,Fthat the governments comments didn't
OL,17,Fgive him any confidence.
OL,19,FMr Castleton, was pursued over a
OL,20,F#25,000 shortfall at his branch in
OL,21,F2004 that he didn't steal.
